init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a mug that says "#1 Dad" on it, and it's a mug that I've always thought was a bit silly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look at the mug again, and it's true.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I look at the other mugs, and they're all changing too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Because she'll be really upset if she thinks she's not the best mom in the world."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "But she's not the best mom in the world," Ben says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "She's not even the best mom in this house."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Well, you're the best dad in this house," Ben says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "And I'm the best kid in this house."
